{"tid":2500890,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"依家其實興用啲咩袋","createTime":"2021-04-23T03:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T04:03:11.000Z","uid":307910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a9351b1c8fcca06910cbc68af6c80da5333b2d6f","tid":2500890,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"平時放假出街好多時都唔戴袋，電話銀包紙巾放晒係條褲或者衫袋，但最近多多機會要帶電腦或者戴書出街，唔想下下再一隻手揸住嘢搭巴士地鐵，想問下大家依家其實興帶咩袋出街<br />\n<br />\n如果背囊嚟講係咪仲興帶藍花袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一直以嚟都好想要一個細細地20L 嘅藍花袋，定係其實已經out撚咗，無人會再孭出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者有時想方便啲，唔駛下下開拉鏈，有時可能會帶啲環保袋，但成日都比啲朋友笑鳩我啲cheap cheap／贈品環保袋，想問下邊度買可以無咁失禮，nico and... 好似都算多人孭出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下你兩個係咪都ok架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f926c49cb5382a2115858cb2a72d0ca6102bc37","tid":2500890,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"百寶袋"},{"pid":"fe22f1627a02fa649cd1a5da650967c9c54a33ae","tid":2500890,"uid":49258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"春袋"},{"pid":"d9bb05b7bf34db3422b43bc9e22028866f90bc11","tid":2500890,"uid":38891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"紅白藍"},{"pid":"7ed66f6d5388fd4914d7751a79ec15e67fa1e483","tid":2500890,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"supreme"},{"pid":"41fce9d8e11904fa6ce0fcc488bcb27bf583313c","tid":2500890,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:54:34.000Z","msg":"我開係潮流台都咁多人亂答嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547271ed316cef1fc1469f7a25e291edd256da55","tid":2500890,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:55:07.000Z","ms